Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were out late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to waste a chance like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for popular voice actresses, opportunities for photo books don't pop up too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doing that kind of work before I become popular as a voice actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be more popular, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of this as a stepping stone towards that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to be a voice actress, you can do that after you get as popular as an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do another thing like the "Sacred Visual Girls School" ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your lousy singing voice, you've got such good offers coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you refuse an offer like this, it'll be very hard to make a living as a voice actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world isn't that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere is heavy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been in a huff for two weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's painstaking work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be on your best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is that girl assistant cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as cute as you, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that if she was, I {\i1}would{\i0} need to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if the atmosphere will change just because I invited Miyoshi over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already tried turning on the radio and the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this may be sudden, but this is my classmate and the person I'm going out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyoshi Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kato. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ogawa. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one working in the middle is Takahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa, sorry to interrupt, but she can do inking at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to give me work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I can show you what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you teach me, I can do anything you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use me for other tasks, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it just became more suffocating having another person in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too quiet in here for six people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.08,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to, like, be more congenial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, but I have no idea what to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an adult appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to start out with a personal topic like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live with my girlfriend, and she's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living together, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're not getting married yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.28,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have several jobs.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pull in a decent income, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will the baby be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a ways off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a boy or a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:26.90,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for calling you over so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised at Ogawa though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's assisting other authors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Monday and Tuesday he assists the author of {\i1}Shounen 3.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard since he's gonna be a daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now too, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me your TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you won at the New Year's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a meeting with our editor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Successful people sure are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not successful yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when he suddenly brought his girlfriend over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having another girl around was a bit relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've got more people, I can give you more time to work on your own project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just being an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Just go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I went to a technical school for manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since then, I've been told I have no talent for writing stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw, but I can't write.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I polished my skills as an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're great, Ogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can learn a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to your assistants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's talk about your fourth chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi, have you thought of a rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm thinking of a detective who tries to arrest the protagonist, like Zenigata from Lupin III... {tl note: detective from Lupin III}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't very shounen-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just having a rival makes everything more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why wait till the fourth chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should introduce him earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to touch the chapters that Hattori approved and submitted to the serialization committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're kicked out by your 3rd chapter, it's his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're going to start revising your story in the fourth chapter based on reviews of the previous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So prepare two different storyboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the first does well, go with that plotline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't, then change it to option two for the next chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If it doesn't"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura, what's your honest opinion of chapter three?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be blunt. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're not brutally honest with each other, we can't call this a business meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also think it's the best one so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how should I put this? Once you have a popular manga, you can play around with it a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at the beginning, everyone is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have any room to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like a bit more fluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're bringing the story to a conclusion in the first three chapters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you had no space to play around with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why chapter three is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's not much to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori's diligence shines through, and it's tightly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps too much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still an underling, so I think the way he did it is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the manga changes slightly according to the preferences of the editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think it can be popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that serialization continues?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're doing it, we have to think it'll be a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the people making it don't think it's good, it definitely won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there will be people who enjoy our work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take pride in that, and it'll encourage you to make the story even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking {\i1}TRAP{\i0}  seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make up two different storyboards for chapter four like he suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No email again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Miyoshi tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have until the end of the month to make a decision about the photo book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't talked to her lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll call her tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make myself useful as an author's assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do? Should I warn him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's about the effectiveness of this panel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it hard to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to grasp the meaning of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going, you two? The last train's departing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with today's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Takahama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some left?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kato, but can you split the rest with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the rate he works, he can handle the rest of it no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get tomorrow's work ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good evening! {she lit says "I'll be going on home now" but there's only so many times you can say I'm going home now and have it not be stupid}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahama, you can go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take what's left and finish it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll finish up today's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll stay here a bit longer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Disney.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work at Disney.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disney...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that if you aim to be a manga artist, you should dream big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you bring that up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you for your work ethic, working on a serialization while still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those two who just left are no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're satisfied just being assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it. {I think this fits}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa's taken assisting to another level, and since he's skilled, I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kato's satisfied with herself just being an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to work hard, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to call me "Sensei".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll call you Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the other two that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell them yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of manga do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like {\i1}Ashita no Joe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe? It's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real "man's manga".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You talked with Takahama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a lively conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't finish inking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also important to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to our office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to finish before they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I'm done with the classroom chores, I'll head right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to ask about Azuki.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for me, it's too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh, he'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's short!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least she responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually don't want her to do it, but I don't want to tell her that flat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Azuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, would Azuki even joke about wanting me to see her naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't she pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Negishi suddenly started singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your boyfriend's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi! Can I talk to you for a minute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a confession?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He'd have to fight for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell Saiko Azuki's address?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he looked pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that! You called her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said if she doesn't do this, she might not get any work as a voice actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's been suffering alone all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I realize it sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been acting strange a lot, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're abandoning the manuscript to go on a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our first serialized chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "If my dream comes true" a million times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think it takes to get to Azuki's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't proceed with the manuscript. our assistants will have nothing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't answer her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going because I don't know what happened and I can't talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi, call Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I've been trying, but she won't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the house line?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it. But I think her mom will answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, this is Takagi, a classmate of Azuki's from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I  have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, you've got a call from Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to talk, answer the phone and tell them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting Miho on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're listening, so I'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko is heading to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's ignoring the manuscript he has to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're fine with that, then I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.93,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The door is closing. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back and draw the manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi called my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing trouble for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I didn't want to show you what I'm like when I'm depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't answer my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's even worse for you to stop drawing manga because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry back and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Azuki, you're worried about the photo book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's better for me to go and talk to you in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how it'll affect my career as a voice actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you be happy if I made a photo book?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want to see your photo book, but I wouldn't want other people to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want it all for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I should be doing something different with my career.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.21,0:19:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I looked at our elementary school yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked at where I wrote my dream for the future — a voice actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was a job called "voice actress", and I genuinely wanted to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to preserve that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in elementary school, I admired manga authors, and I sketched a ton of manga in my school notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I gave up on it when I learned the harsh reality of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a person who tried too hard making manga, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing how that world works, I realize that if I step into it, my ideals and reality might change and even be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the road is the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think there are people who will realize their dreams without being crushed, no matter what obstacle is in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'll improve bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to you helped me sort out my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better now, so don't worry and draw your manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from now on, lets talk about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being stubborn and acting tough, even while I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're the one who said "Lets try hard and encourage each other".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't talk, I can't encourage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, let's go to the beach one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take lots of pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise for when our dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's a promise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dreams keep increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just talking about dreams doesn't make them a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem okay now, so I'm gonna hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for interrupting your chance at a date, Saiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Shuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come back and pen-in the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho making a photo book, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in the end, she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she continue her voice actress work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she got another call to audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sent me a email.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she asked me to properly apologize to Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were really fearsome that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it all went well after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly, {\i1}TRAP{\i0}  safely began its first serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's finally begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just have to wait and see how it does in the polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a first chapter of a new series should get first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll have the early results, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of TRAP's serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.96,0:24:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about the ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and other things, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix up any problems with my team!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, let me call you "boss"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Window and Snow."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my body is freezing, my dreams won't cool down!
